    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207061</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Our Changing Voices</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Unsere Ändernden Stimmen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Nos Voix Changeantes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Nossas Vozes Em mudança</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le Nostre Voci Cambianti</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Οι μεταβαλλόμενες φωνές μας</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Nuestras Voces Que cambian</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">is a lesson in which students identify issues involved in a family or community's migration into Nebraska. Students then examine the history of their own families.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">ist eine Lektion, in der Kursteilnehmer die 
Ausgaben kennzeichnen, die in eine Familie oder der Gemeinschaft 
Migration in Nebraska mit einbezogen werden. Kursteilnehmer 
überprüfen dann die Geschichte ihrer eigenen Familien.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">est une leçon dans laquelle les étudiants 
identifient des issues impliquées dans un transfert de famille ou de 
communauté en le Nébraska. Les étudiants examinent alors 
l'histoire de leurs propres familles.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">é uma lição em que os estudantes identificam as
edições envolvidas em uma migração da família ou da comunidade em
Nebraska. Os estudantes examinam então o history de suas 
próprias famílias.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">è una lezione in cui gli allievi identificano le 
edizioni coinvolgere in un'espansione della Comunità o della famiglia
in Nebraska. Gli allievi allora esaminano la storia delle loro 
proprie famiglie.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">είναι ένα μάθημα στο οποίο οι σπουδαστές 
προσδιορίζουν τα ζητήματα που περιλαμβάνονται σε μια μετανάστευση 
οικογενειών ή της κοινότητας στη Νεμπράσκα. Οι σπουδαστές 
εξετάζουν έπειτα την ιστορία των οικογενειών τους.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">es una lección en la cual los estudiantes 
identifican las ediciones implicadas en una migración de la familia o
de la comunidad en Nebraska. Los estudiantes entonces examinan 
la historia de sus propias familias.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
